			                		<div class="panel-body">
			                    		<p>In Smart Track, Guard Tour Patrols consist of a series of fixed or roaming checkpoints which officers must complete during their shift. Every route created can be easily activated, assigned or changed from the Route Library. For fixed routes, a pre-set order and schedule are required, ensuring that officers complete the route in a specific order and complete each checkpoint in a specific time frame.  Checkpoint order and route duration can be changed quickly and easily by resizing, dragging or dropping them on the intuitive scheduling feature.</p>
